description: If you love coconut then you will love these biscuits.
keywords: Biscuit,Pescatarian,Halal,Seafood free,Soy free,Vegetarian,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Quick & easy dessert,Peanut free
name: Coconut Biscuits Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to a moderate temperature. Spray a baking tray with nonstick spray and line with baking paper.

Cream butter and sugar unit soft and light, beat in egg and add the flour, coconut mix well. Roll teaspoon of mixture into balls and flatten between palms. Place on baking tray, leaving room for spreading. Using the back of a fork flatten out the biscuits leaving marks on the biscuits.
Place the baking tray in the oven and bake for 1215 minutes or until golden brown. When cooked place on a cooling rack.
